      • validateTransaction

        public boolean validateTransaction(TransferTransaction transaction)
                            throws BankAccountNotExistsException,
                                   CurrencyNotSupportException,
                                   InvalidMoneyAmountException
        validate if all fields in the transaction is correct base on business logic
        Parameters:
        transaction - the target transaction to be validated
        Returns:
        true if there is no errors
        Throws:
        BankAccountNotExistsException - when bank account for sender or receiver not exists
        CurrencyNotSupportException - if currency to transfer is not supported
        InvalidMoneyAmountException - if the money amount is invalid eg. sender has no sufficient fund
